      "content": "hey i've been dealing with this crazy bad lower back pain all day and i already took like 800mg of ibuprofen an hour ago but it's not doing anything. it's like a stabbing feeling. can i take some aspirin too or maybe even a higher dose of the ibu to make it stop? i really need to sleep",
